{"tid":2412742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九人「和你Lunch」被控非法集結等罪提堂 維修技工被控管有螺絲批獲無條件撤控 其餘轉區院審理","createTime":"2021-02-18T08:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T11:26:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e90217928bbffb1349cf273affa053827b93ee3","tid":2412742,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"網民前年11月發起連日三罷，七男兩女事後被捕，日前被落案起訴非法集結及管有工具意圖損毀財產等罪，案件今在東區裁判法院提堂。其中一名男維修技工獲控方無條件撤控，其餘被告的案件將轉介區域法院審理。主任裁判官錢禮押後案件至4月12日以準備轉介文件，各被告獲准以1,000元保釋，須交出所有旅遊證件、於報住地點居住、每星期向警署報到一次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/5SJ2K2JIIBEFZARKKQYGECPM5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2F5SJ2K2JIIBEFZARKKQYGECPM5A%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=bc5c794c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2F5SJ2K2JIIBEFZARKKQYGECPM5A%2F&h=e858c953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/5SJ2K2JIIBEFZARKKQYGECPM5A/</a>"},{"pid":"2eaf81dbacda4be1f3bee7010d03f15cd46379d7","tid":2412742,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b87231e82561fa68b7b95b351c10d8c4c4dedb0","tid":2412742,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"咁都踢去區院"},{"pid":"0c9ed5c52162ce6eaf29309890c88531f6cc7b5a","tid":2412742,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eaf81dbacda4be1f3bee7010d03f15cd46379d7","tid":2412742,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/